m-color: #000000; border-bottom-style: solid; background-color: #ccc;">  se=
en buyers who want to get out of mergers before</a>, and she has seen Musk=
=E2=80=99s claims so far. =E2=80=9CI am reticent to say more concerning the=
 merits of the counterclaims at this posture before they have been fully li=
tigated,=E2=80=9D she wrote in today=E2=80=99s opinion.=C2=A0=E2=80=9CThe w=
orld will have to wait for the post-trial decision.=E2=80=9D=C2=A0</p>
